   "source": [
    "# 🔬 Module 3 — Eye Disease Classification\n",
    "**Full Pipeline: Data → Train → Evaluate → Grad-CAM → Report**\n",
    "\n",
    "### Architecture: EfficientNet-B4 (pretrained on ImageNet)\n",
    "### Dataset: All folders on Google Drive unified into 10 classes\n",
    "\n",
    "| Class | Source |\n",
    "|-------|--------|\n",
    "| normal | datasets/normal + dataset/1_normal |\n",
    "| cataract | datasets/cataract + dataset/2_cataract |\n",
    "| glaucoma | datasets/glaucoma + dataset/2_glaucoma |\n",
    "| diabetic_retinopathy | datasets/diabetes |\n",
    "| age_macular_degeneration | datasets/ageDegeneration |\n",
    "| hypertension | datasets/hypertension |\n",
    "| myopia | datasets/myopia |\n",
    "| other_retina | datasets/others + dataset/3_retina_disease |\n",
    "| rop_normal | image/Normal |\n",
    "| rop_disease | image/Stage1 + Stage2 + Stage3 + laser scars |"
   ]
  },
